collaboration proposal), RECRUITMENT (job inquiry or recruiter outreach), SPAM (irrelevant, mass outreach, or bot), OTHER (anything else). Return the category, a confidence score between 0 and 1, and a short reason. Respond with JSON only."},"promptType":"define","hasOutputParser":true},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"0a0f3093-5f2c-42b8-8f22-8c2a4fd24615","name":"Group - Receive webhook and normalize payload","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[0,1344],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":724,"height":392,"content":"## Receive webhook and normalize payload\n\nReceives the incoming LinkedIn message from Unipile, responds immediately, sets the auto-send config default, and extracts/normalizes the relevant fields from the webhook payload."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"2e753dc0-4bbd-4f2b-8d41-c96024d57bf4","name":"Group - Validate sender and fetch conversation history","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[752,1280],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":680,"height":524,"content":"## Validate sender and fetch conversation history\n\nFilters for genuine inbound company-page messages (not spam, not self-sent), then fetches the last 6 messages and formats them into a chronological transcript. Fetch errors are logged to Airtable."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"cde31aaf-1fb2-4e67-bac6-91fe8e843c21","name":"Group - Classify message and check for spam","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1456,1200],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":632,"height":680,"content":"## Classify message and check for spam\n\nClassifies the message's intent (LEAD/SUPPORT/PARTNERSHIP/RECRUITMENT/SPAM/OTHER) using Claude via OpenRouter with shared session memory, then routes spam messages to a dedicated Airtable log (Log Spam sits just to the right, sharing this cluster)."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"89718562-5363-4128-bd23-5302da68ace8","name":"Group - Generate grounded reply via Pinecone","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[2112,1392],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":420,"height":696,"content":"## Generate grounded reply via Pinecone\n\nGenerates the reply using the same shared Claude model and session memory from classification, grounding every answer in the Pinecone knowledge base via a retrieval tool with matching Gemini embeddings."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"9ab0fd55-2be4-40a5-8bdf-b0171642aa51","name":"Group - Save draft and check auto-send toggle","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[2544,1408],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":460,"height":412,"content":"## Save draft and check auto-send toggle\n\nUpserts the AI draft into Airtable Drafts (matched by chat_id, so a conversation updates in place instead of duplicating) and checks the workflow's auto-send configuration."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"880c8583-2db8-4e43-bac8-e06b521b01ef","name":"Group - Send approved reply and log outcome","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[3024,1408],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":558,"height":484,"content":"## Send approved reply and log outcome\n\nSends the reply via Unipile when auto-send is on, then marks the draft sent or logs a send error to Airtable."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"7da366eb-905b-4374-a580-b269dc2a5b9d","name":"Update Draft Status Sent1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.airtable","position":[3392,1536],"parameters":{"base":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"appQvM6vBl23Vw171","cachedResultName":"LinkedIn RAG Bot"},"table":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"tblPkjkyXfsHq5aa5","cachedResultName":"Drafts"},"columns":{"value":{"status":"sent","chat_id":"={{ $('Extract & Normalize Fields').item.json.chat_id }}","sent_at":"={{ $now.toISO() }}"},"schema":[{"id":"id","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"readOnly":true,"required":false,"displayName":"id","defaultMatch":true},{"id":"sender_name","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"readOnly":false,"required":false,"displayName":"sender_name","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"sender_id","type":"string","display":true,"removed":true,"readOnly":false,"required":false,"d